  <p class="hero-lede">Sun-soaked steals, island-wide.</p>
  <div class="filters-bar" aria-label="Categories">
    <a class="pill" href="/?category=hotel">ğŸ¨ Hotels</a>
    <a class="pill" href="/?category=restaurant">ğŸ½ï¸ Dining</a>
    <a class="pill" href="/?category=experience">ğŸŒŠ Experiences</a>
    <a class="pill" href="/?category=flight">âœˆï¸ Flights</a>
  </div>
  <div class="ticker" aria-live="polite">âœ¨ <%= newDealsCount %> new deals today â€¢ Last updated <%= updatedAt %></div>
  <div style="margin-top:1rem;">
